author: ypenghui6
content: Does anyone know if ERC-4337 has been implemented yet?

author: eikix
content: It has been implemented yes, companies are running the infra (e.g. Biconomy, Pimlico, Alchemy, Cometh, etc.), wallets are building on top of it too (e.g. Safe, Zerodev, Coinbase wallet). It is somewhat still a work in progress in term of standard

author: eikix

Nope, this is abstracted away by SDKs such as biconomy or permissionless JS
Bundler infra is done by external actors

Note that this is probably the wrong channel to discuss this
